These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, skateboard, train
4 different pets are kept: horse, rat, pony, bird
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person driving the ship is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Transport          | train | skateboard | roller | ship   |
| Pet   | rat  | horse     | pony   | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, doctor, journalist, firefighter
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, swisher, havana, ritmeester
1. the firefighter is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
3. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the firefighter is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | journalist | firefighter | doctor | dressmaker    |
| Cigar   | havana    | swisher      | pall-mall | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, tower
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, coach, chef
1. the coach is on the left of the chef##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the bartender##1
3. the electrician is on the far right##1
4. the chef is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the colonial house is on the left of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| House         | gothic-revival | tower | colonial   | farmhouse |
| Job   | bartender   | coach | chef | electrician         |

