.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, tiparillo, chaman, aristoff
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, poker, canasta
1. the person playing monopoly is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | tiparillo | game  | chaman      |
| Game         | monopoly | canasta   | poker | mah-jongg |

