.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, tiparillo, bongani
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, reading, board-games
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | bongani | tiparillo | aristoff | baccarat |
| Hobby           | camping      | reading | board-games | card-games    |

