.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, marigold, begonia
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, colombian, malaysian
1. the colombian is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
4. the japanese is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Flower   | marigold | poppy | azalea | begonia  |
| Nationality           | colombian | pakistani | malaysian       | japanese |

