.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, sunflower, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Flower         | sunflower | lily      | azalea | amaryllis |
| Birthday   | september          | april | december     | march    |

