.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, handball, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, orchid, azalea, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | parkour    | handball       | ice-hockey | weightlifting   |
| Flower     | orchid | azalea | zinnia   | daisy |

