.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, spinach, potato, grapefruit
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, whist, scrabble
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Food    | cabbage | potato  | spinach | grapefruit |
| Game   | scrabble | whist | bridge          | chess    |

