.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, february, june
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, havana, blend
1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Birthday      | february | july  | november | june |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | havana | blend           | bluemaster   |

