.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, punk, country, blues
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, water, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of punk##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | indie | blues | country  |
| Beverage           | cola | juice      | water | lemonade |

