2. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan of country##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | december      | may | march | july |
| Music-Genre     | folk | ambient    | dubstep  | country |

