.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, roller, train
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, soy-milk, coffee
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Transport         | jet-ski | roller | train | subway |
| Beverage   | coffee     | soy-milk    | iced-tea      | milk   |

