.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
City: venice, marseilles, london, new-york
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, tiparillo, fonseca, bluemaster
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City   | venice | london | marseilles | new-york   |
| Cigar     | fonseca  | montecristo    | tiparillo       | bluemaster |

 